{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"常數","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Grammar_and_types_e5a53691c318855e3342ad91feb78f2e","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常數","title":"常數","isH3":true,"content":"<p>你可以使用 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/const\" title=\"en/Core_JavaScript_1.5_Reference/Statements/const\">const</a></code> 關鍵字建立唯讀的常數。常數識別子的語法和變數識別子的相同︰以字母或底線開頭，可以包含字母、數值、底線字元。</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">const prefix = '212';\n</pre>\n<p>在 Script 執行時，常數不可以藉由代入或重新宣告來改變值。</p>\n<p>常數的作用域規則和變數一樣，除了 <code>const</code> 關鍵字即使是全域常數也一直是必要的。如果省略了關鍵字，識別子就會被認定為變數。</p>\n<p>你不可以在同一個作用域裡，使用和函數或變數的同樣的名稱來宣告常數。例如︰</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">// 這會引起錯誤\nfunction f() {};\nconst f = 5;\n\n// 這也會引起錯誤\nfunction f() {\n  const g = 5;\n  var g;\n\n  //其他語句\n}\n</pre>\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/變數\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/字面表達\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"你可以使用 const 關鍵字建立唯讀的常數。常數識別子的語法和變數識別子的相同︰以字母或底線開頭，可以包含字母、數值、底線字元。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Grammar and types","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/grammar_and_types_e5a53691c318855e3342ad91feb78f2e","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/grammar_and_types_e5a53691c318855e3342ad91feb78f2e/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Grammar_and_types_e5a53691c318855e3342ad91feb78f2e","title":"常數"}],"pageTitle":"常數 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}